<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw zan chimum ah i um ui,
 Meipi chuh a hung zing hi;
 Enin, I kinep zing khuo chuh,
 Tun vanah vak ding ei tai;
 Zion tang sang chung apata,
 Galvengte aw I zak tieng,
 Lawp takin kikhawm hiting un-
 Lalpen hung tieng leh.

[V2]
 Aw Zion; Aw Zion;
 Na zawhna lopi ding Lalpen hung tieng leh,
 Aw Zion; Aw Zion,
 Chawihsan in um tan la, Lalpen hung tieng leh.

[V3]
 2. Jehovah, tatdawk sate haw,
 Suoh lam leh Tum lam apat;
 Lawp leh nuomsan hungkhawm untin,
 Chawlhna tiem chuh chang dingin;
 Tieng chuleh zattin leh nam tin,
 Gam tina te nunnuom in,
 Lawp takin kikhawm hiting un-
 Lalpen hung tieng leh.

[V4]
 3. Sun leh zan a ginum a ngak in,
 A hung tieng ei mu hen;
 Lal na I sepna chiet u ah,
 I galvan teu val zing in;
 I thaumei teu gaw zo diem in,
 Thieng takin vak sak hitiu;

[V5]
 4. Aw, Hukdampa hung kin mengin,
 Semgim ten a ngaklah ui
 Bangtik leh ka hun mu ding um,
 Na van gam khawpi vak tawh?
 Na kumsawt mi thiengtho te leh -
 Namtin Na hukdamte tawh,
 Nang mah paka nawpla sak khawm-
 Kal ka ngak lah ui.

[V6]
 Lawptaka I kikhawp theihna'n-
 Lalpen hung tieng leh.</lyrics>
<title>WHEN THE KING SHALL COME</title>
</song>